{"type": "article", "id": 19219, "title": "木质茶几", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-17T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122353btYqsvh5R02JH63y.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利的设计组合 bibi 做了这张有些可爱的木质茶几，三角形的桌面源于自行车的座位。浅色的桌面上没有木头的纹饰，只在侧面勾出深浅相间横条的纹路，三个角上分别有三颗钉子，在简单的造型中有活泼的气质。茶几使用了 2.2 厘米厚的胶合板，可以承受一定的重量。<a href=\"http://bidesignbi.com/sella-sellino/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145818YqkzV7KSfmT28PX1.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145818aq4lJFVzk9pcDnYN.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1413\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.30833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145819fC295DmMYprEkHho.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}